This topic describes how to use the Harbor integration for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

##<a id='using'></a> Using Harbor

To log in to Harbor, go to https://<i>harbor_host_address</i>:443 in a browser and log in as user **admin**, using the password that you set when you configured Harbor for PCF. 

For information about how to use Harbor, see the following sections of the [Harbor User Guide](https://github.com/vmware/harbor/blob/master/docs/user_guide.md).

- [Role Based Access Control (RBAC)](https://github.com/vmware/harbor/blob/master/docs/user_guide.md#role-based-access-controlrbac)
